node.title: Police investigating after fatality at a workplace in Gisborne
node.description: A man has died following a workplace incident at Awapuni in Gisborne.
node.content:
["A man has died following a workplace incident at Awapuni in Gisborne.", "", "
\nPhoto: 123rf.com\n
", "Emergency services were called to an address on Stanley Road about 11:15am.", "WorkSafe has been notified.", "Police will be investigating on behalf of the Coroner.", "No other information has been provided."]
